title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 25 2022
description:
What can he say? A preview of Biden's State of the Union speech. PSA for P-P-P-S: Post-Pandemic Paranoia Syndrome. Joy Behar worries that Ukraine war will interfere with her trip to Italy. What comedians do Clay and Buck like these days? C&B take calls to end the week.
